The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Pension hike

 New 

 Delhi, Nov. 9 (PTI): Freedom fighters and their spouses 

 would now get an enhanced pension of around Rs 10,000 per 

 month effective October 2. 

 The decision to enhance the basic pension of freedom fighters and the basic dependent family pension of spouses of deceased freedom fighters by an amount of Rs 2,330 per month was taken by the Centre today, finance minister P. Chidambaram said. 




